<TEXT>
<P>
Wedding bells are on hold again for Laker star Magic Johnson, who said his 
wedding, which had been scheduled for Sept. 1, was indefinitely postponed. 
</P>
<P>
Johnson is engaged to Earletha Kelly, 31, of Detroit. 
</P>
<P>
"We're still together and everything, but we're just going to wait," Johnson 
said. "We're still going to get married, probably in Lansing." 
</P>
<P>
He didn't say why the wedding was put off, but added the plans had been 
postponed before. 
</P>
