of China's production and packaging facilities in March and April. DOUGLAS R. 
BURROWS / For The Times; Photo, . . .and products China would like to export to 
U.S. WILL YURMAN / For The Times; Photo, Consultant Robert McMath, left, of the 
New Products Showcase &amp; Learning Center, . . . 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
