La Salle in the Persian Gulf. Reuters; Photo, Beating the deadline -- A tanker 
loaded with Iraqi oil docks at a refinery in Paulsboro, N.J. The ship, with 
about 1 million barrels of oil, is the first to arrive since the United States 
embargoed Iraqi oil. Associated Press; Map, YANBU, Saudi Arabia, AP/Los Angeles 
Times 
</P>
